text: Bence Demeter (born 20 March 1990) is a Hungarian modern pentathlete. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the men's event. ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian male modern pentathletes Category:Olympic modern pentathletes of Hungary Category:Modern pentathletes at the 2016 Summer Olympics
